description: For sale: $197,700. Charm and tranquility abound on this 7+ acre hobby farm! Spacious farmhouse style 2-story home features 5 bedrooms and 2 baths. The open kitchen/dining area offers a center island and abundant cabinetry for storage, plus there's a walk-thru pantry just a step away. Relax in the living/family room with its heated tile flooring and a wood stove for those crisp winter evenings. Plus there's a main-floor laundry, main floor bedroom (which might also serve as an office or den if preferred), and 4 more nice-sized bedrooms and a full bath on the upper level. A detached 2-stall garage also includes a separate 26x30 heated shop area. Plus older barn, chicken coop, grain bin and other outbuildings. Nice woods and open grass/pasture areas. Bring your animals or outdoor toys! Or just walk the woods and enjoy the peaceful quiet of the countryside.
For sale: $12,500. Property is being sold as is, where is.
